Class VehicleClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.model.VehicleClass

  • public final class VehicleClass
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an in game vehicle class. This class is fully annotated with JAXB for easy XML conversion.
